commands: jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"electron-forge-maker-appimage@github:SpacingBat3/electron-forge-maker-appimage": "flatpak-node/git-packages/electron-forge-maker-appimage-162cde3428951c6237a6d84fdf97ff70dc2e0b6f#162cde3428951c6237a6d84fdf97ff70dc2e0b6f"}' 'walk(    if type == "object"    then        to_entries | map(            if (.value | type == "string") and $data[.value]            then .value = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.value])"            else .            end        ) | from_entries    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package.json.new

jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"git+ssh://git@github.com/SpacingBat3/electron-forge-maker-appimage.git#162cde3428951c6237a6d84fdf97ff70dc2e0b6f": "flatpak-node/git-packages/electron-forge-maker-appimage-162cde3428951c6237a6d84fdf97ff70dc2e0b6f#162cde3428951c6237a6d84fdf97ff70dc2e0b6f"}' 'walk(    if type == "object" and (.version | type == "string") and $data[.version]    then        .version = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.version])"    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json.new
